(9, 'hpil._.1111', 'Primavera Training ', 'Management Training', ' This primavera P6 professional training leads you through the entire project life cycle, from planning to execution.  You will develop a thorough understanding of how to plan and schedule.  Enrolling in this course will help you understand P6 professional\'s basic features and functionality so you can apply them to your organization \'S project management processes. You will also learn how to time and within budget to ensure optimal outcomes from capital and resources investments.  Course objectives *     Work Breakdown Structure *     Define Roles & Resources *     Assign Role/Resources *     Create Project Adding Activities *     Working with P6 *     Calenders *     Analyze the Project Plan *     Understand Data…', '320', '166939230865205Gplatinum Training Primavera Training.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
(10, 'hpil._.2443', 'Microsoft Project Training ', 'Management Training', 'This training will teach you how to manage and control many projects for your business more effectively.  You will learn how to use Project\'s versatile and user-friendly tools and solutions to create the Project plan, track progress, adjust resources, and present dynamic reports. This training will enable managers and individuals to achieve project outcomes faster with high-quality and within budget. At the end of this course, you will learn how to help team plan and prioritize tasks, assign resources, track progress and budget to complete projects more efficiently.', '80000', '1669392378373701Gplatinum Training Microsoft Project.jpg', 'Physical Training'),
(11, 'hpil._.1111', 'Basic Excel Training', 'Management Training', 'Introduction to Microsoft Excel training empowers participants with key skills to create and edit worksheets, formulas and functions, and sort and filter detailed data with tables and slicers.What you will learn: *     Efficiently navigate and manipulate worksheets and workbooks. *     Implement an income and expense statement with formulas, functions, and names. *     Design and reusable data entry template that protects formulas. *     Implement conditional formatting to analyse sales information *     Connect, prepare, and validate data employing editing tools, formulas, and flash fill.   *     Identify, sort, and select detailed data with tables and slicers. *     Present and analyse data with conditional formatting, chatting, Sparkline’s, and printing parameters, *     Construct IF functions that make decisions-present results visually. *     Combine data with 3-D formulas. *     Analyse summary data with pivot Tables and implement a quick dashboard', '70000', '1669392505428955Gplatinum Training Basic excel.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
(12, 'hpil._.2312', 'Advanced Excel Training ', 'Management Training', 'This course is for intermediate to Advanced Excel users.  This course uses multiple mini-projects to teach you how to work with multiple Excel techniques to prepare your sales reports and perform analytics. This course is for intermediate to Advanced Excel users.  This course uses multiple mini-projects to teach you how to work with multiple Excel techniques to prepare your sales reports and perform analytics. 1.     Sales visualization techniques without using Charts 2.     Find correct sales by extracting Bank Account Codes from unclean data dumps 3.     Analysis by Bucket sizes 0-1000, 1001-2000, and so on 4.    Combination Sales ledgers of multiple months & Automate and process for next months 5.    Analyse 3-years\' sales using Pivot Table 6.    Commission Calculation using different incentive period 7.     Allocating sales to different agents 8.     Consolidating Sales of multiple products, multiple agents from different sheets. 9.     After Sales Service Tracking - Contract Expiry Date, TAT & Response Times', '90000', '1669392579482819Gplatinum Training Advanced Excel.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
(13, 'hpil._.2231', 'Advanced Microsoft Word Training ', 'Management Training', 'This course, Microsoft Word Advanced, will provide you with an understanding of the advanced skills used in Microsoft Word.  You will learn about collaborating on document by modifying user information, comparing document changes, and reviewing a document.  You will also learn about inserting ancillary tables and master document.  You will be able to explain adding reference marks and notes,. This includes captions, cross-referencing, bookmarks and hyperlinks.  You will also learn about footnotes and end notes as well as citation and bibliography.  You will learn about blank and cover pages and as well as indexing a document and the table of contents.  This course is rich for you!', '112500', '1669392787623502Gplatinum Training Microsoft Project.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
(14, 'hpil._.2343', 'Basic PowerPoint Training', 'Management Training', 'Starting out in Microsoft Word or need a refresher?  This online course is designed to give you a solid foundation in the basics of word. In powerful engaging lessons you will learn how to format text with fonts and colours, use bullets and indents, customize the Quick Access Toolbar, insert pictures and screenshots, set up page layout for margins and printing and much more. Whether you use Word for work, study or leisure, these tutorials will help you transform that blank page into a professional looking document.', '210000', '1669392810871078Gplatinum Training Basic Powerpoint Training.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
(15, 'hpil._.3232', 'Basic Word Training', 'Management Training', 'Starting out in Microsoft Word or need a refresher?  This online course is designed to give you a solid foundation in the basics of word. In powerful engaging lessons you will learn how to format text with fonts and colours, use bullets and indents, customize the Quick Access Toolbar, insert pictures and screenshots, set up page layout for margins and printing and much more. Whether you use Word for work, study or leisure, these tutorials will help you transform that blank page into a professional looking document.', '210000', '1669392866413669Gplatinum Training Basic Word Training.jpg', 'Virtual Training'),
